When you want your user,
your visitor to select options,

00:13:12.020 --> 00:13:14.260
make life easy for them.

00:13:14.260 --> 00:13:20.470
Multi-select interfaces are
hard, checkboxes are super easy.

00:13:20.470 --> 00:13:23.902
If you have many
options, a searchable,

00:13:23.903 --> 00:13:26.390
