00:14:28.890 --> 00:14:33.800
Click, click,
ready and it stays there.

00:14:33.800 --> 00:14:38.590
It's really, really easy and people
get that so don't use multi-select

00:14:38.590 --> 00:14:41.000
because it's a very
difficult interface.

