00:30:15.970 --> 00:30:17.370
That's super important.

00:30:18.870 --> 00:30:22.390
If people cannot fill out your
form right or don't understand

00:30:22.390 --> 00:30:23.800
what goes wrong, they will leave.

00:30:25.600 --> 00:30:29.450
First, tell the rules in advance.

00:30:30.470 --> 00:30:32.870
How many times did you
