00:30:36.330 --> 00:30:37.810
That's so super annoying.

00:30:37.810 --> 00:30:42.600
You come up with a super password
and you press enter or submit

00:30:42.600 --> 00:30:47.220
and then, "Oh, no, but it has
to be like-- Tell the people

00:30:47.220 --> 00:30:50.330
in advance what the
rules of the password is.

00:30:53.190 --> 00:30:56.870
