00:35:07.075 --> 00:35:11.350
<v Morgan> The main takeaway here
is have empathy for your users,

00:35:11.350 --> 00:35:13.910
and that means all of your users.

00:35:15.840 --> 00:35:18.760
Those who need assistive technology
and those who don't, think

00:35:18.760 --> 00:35:21.590
about absolutely everybody who is
going to be filling out your form

00:35:23.955 --> 00:35:28.650
<v Rian> Don't create anxiety
by not being predictable,

00:35:28.650 --> 00:35:33.340
by giving people too short time,
or doing unexpected things.

00:35:35.230 --> 00:35:36.310
Be trustworthy.

00:35:37.630 --> 00:35:42.620
<v Morgan> Be predictable,
make sure you explain

00:35:42.620 --> 00:35:45.830
what will happen next,
either when a user clicks a button

00:35:45.830 --> 00:35:48.180
to go to the next page or
when they submit the form.

00:35:50.430 --> 00:35:55.600
<v Rian> Form validation
is super important.

00:35:55.600 --> 00:35:58.850
