and error messages.

00:35:59.925 --> 00:36:01.130
<v Morgan> Keep it simple.

00:36:01.130 --> 00:36:05.130
Avoid overcomplicating your forms
and don't make users have to think

00:36:05.130 --> 00:36:10.700
or second guess or cause stress
as they fill out the form.

00:36:12.390 --> 00:36:16.670
